}

<div class="container">

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-responsive" src="~/img/Informatic.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Computers. <span class="text-muted">Do what you love, you'll never work a day in your life.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">I'm a software developer, I am fortunate to have a profession as a hobby also, this facilitates my learning also in my free time.</p>
            <p class="lead">In computer science you can be self-taught and if you are interested in learning I can recommend <a href="https://www.w3schools.com/" target="_blank"><u>w3schools</u></a> and <a href="https://www.tutorialsteacher.com/" target="_blank"><u>tutorialsteacher</u></a>. Any doubts you can also use <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/" target="_blank"><u>stackoverflow</u></a> as a help.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-responsive" src="~/img/Travel.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Travel. <span class="text-muted">Discover the world, Challenge accepted!</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">I love meeting new places, traveling lift my soul and carry energies.</p>
            <p class="lead">Portugal is lovely! The people, the food, the beaches and the weather is amazing but the experience of know new cultures, new people and different mentalities is the most enriching that can exist.</p>
            <blockquote class="blockquote">"Travel is the only thing you buy and that makes you richer".</blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

