        <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-responsive" src="~/img/Nba.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Sports. <span class="text-muted">NBA, I LOVE THIS GAME.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">My favorite sport is basketball, especially the National Basketball Association better known as <a href="https://www.nba.com/" target="_blank"><u>NBA</u></a>. Although the best player ever to be Michael Jordan my current favorite is Kevin Durant.</p>
            <p class="lead">In football I love to see English Premier League, but my heart club is <a href="https://www.slbenfica.pt/" target="_blank" style="color:red;"><u>Sport Lisboa e Benfica.</u></a></p>
