            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Cars. <span class="text-muted">Muscle Cars, Old but Gold.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">I like all kinds of cars, from the oldest burning diesel up until new electric one's. My dream is one day have a 1969 Ford Mustang recovered by me.</p>
        </div>
